			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Load BGO_Main. From debug book Quest flags and options -> Act3 -> Danthelon Dancing Axe -> Add Jaheira as companion.\r\nDialog with Jaheira starts, accept her as companion.\r\nTeleport to larian://bookmark?name=BGO_DanthelonDancingAxe_Basement&mod=GustavDev&level=BGO_Main_A&camPos=-20.376675;45.939648;125.109711&camTarget=-19.833111;45.491306;125.819305\r\nCome closer to harper npcs, combat starts. Kill real harper and then every enemy. Use SwD on harper's corpse."
				},
